Gloria Asumnu (amụrụ na 22 Mee 1985) bụ onye Naijirịa na-agba ọsọ
Dị ka a mụrụ ya na United States, ọ nọchitere anya ha na asọmpi mba ụwa, tupu ọ gbanwee ịnọchite anya Naijirịa
Ọ gbanwere mba n'afọ 2011, na akwụkwọ nke abụọ ya, nke mbụ IAAF jụrụ.
A mụrụ ya na Houston, Texas, ọ gbara ọsọ maka Alief Elsik High School na Mahadum Tulane.
